Package: rapporteur
Type: Package
Title: Reports on triple billion data
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Elliott", "Messeiller", , "elliott.messeiller@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Reports on the Triple Billion data calculated by the billionaiRe
    package. Allows to export country and regional summary Excel sheets, plots,
    and more.
